titleabbrev
Element


titleabbrev
&titleabbrev.purpose;


&titleabbrev.synopsis.gen;
Description



TitleAbbrev holds an abbreviated version of a
Title.  One common use of TitleAbbrev is
for the text used in running headers or footers, when the proper
title is too long to be used conveniently.


Processing expectations


&format.context; Abbreviated titles are usually used only in specific
contexts, such as headers and footers, and suppressed everywhere else.



